name: Dango Dash
overview: Help Dango make the people in his village happy in this light-hearted retro platformer for the Game Boy Color. Features: Snappy platforming through imaginative environments A mix of traditional platforming and Zelda-like adventuring Quest-driven story advanced by helping each villager A kickass soundtrack by Scott Semanski (https://soundcloud.com/scottsemanski) Stylish 2.5D graphics full of character
